OL,3,CEsther Ghey: Ofcom online safety rules
OL,4,Cneed to be 'less ambiguous'
OL,6,FThe draft codes also require firms to
OL,7,Fhave content moderation systems and
OL,8,Fprocesses in place, and ensure that
OL,9,Fswift action is taken against harmful
OL,10,Fcontent. Search engines are expected
OL,11,Fto have a "safe search" option for use
OL,12,Fby children.
OL,14,FAlongside the regulations being mooted
OL,15,Fby Ofcom, Brianna's mother also called
OL,16,Ffor tech firms to produce a smartphone
OL,17,Fdesigned for children - one that
OL,18,Frestricts content for users.
