OL,3,CEsther Ghey: Ofcom online safety rules
OL,4,Cneed to be 'less ambiguous'
OL,6,F"The regulator has proposed some
OL,7,Fimportant and welcome measures, but
OL,8,Fits overall set of proposals need to
OL,9,Fbe more ambitious to prevent children
OL,10,Fencountering harmful content that cost
OL,11,FMolly's life.
OL,13,F"It's over six years since Molly's
OL,14,Fdeath, but the reality is that very
OL,15,Flittle has yet changed. In some
OL,16,Frespects, the risks for teens have
OL,17,Factually got worse.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
