OL,4,Cneed to be 'less ambiguous'
OL,6,FSir Peter Wanless, chief executive of
OL,7,Fchildren's charity, the NSPCC, said
OL,8,Fthe draft code was a "welcome step in
OL,9,Fthe right direction" towards
OL,10,Fprotecting children online.
OL,12,F"The draft codes set appropriate, high
OL,13,Fstandards and make it clear that all
OL,14,Ftech companies will have work to do to
OL,15,Fmeet Ofcom's expectations for keeping
OL,16,Fchildren safe," he said.
