OL,3,CEsther Ghey: Ofcom online safety rules
OL,4,Cneed to be 'less ambiguous'
OL,6,F"Tech companies will be legally
OL,7,Frequired to make sure their platforms
OL,8,Fare fundamentally safe by design for
OL,9,Fchildren when the final code comes
OL,10,Finto effect, and we urge them to get
OL,11,Fahead of the curve now and take
OL,12,Fimmediate action to prevent
OL,13,Finappropriate and harmful content from
OL,14,Fbeing shared with children and young
OL,15,Fpeople."
