OL,6,FTechnology Secretary, Michelle
OL,7,FDonelan, said: "When we passed the
OL,8,FOnline Safety Act last year, we went
OL,9,Ffurther than almost any other country
OL,10,Fin our bid to make the UK the safest
OL,11,Fplace to be a child online.
OL,13,F"Once in place, these measures will
OL,14,Fbring in a fundamental change in how
OL,15,Fchildren in the UK experience the
OL,16,Fonline world. I want to assure parents
OL,17,Fthat protecting children is our number
OL,18,Fone priority and these laws will help
OL,19,Fkeep their families safe.
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@AOU
